{
  "stem": "9230.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was so strong, the bombs has so much power, we was a few hundred girls and men, and we was holding the door.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was impossible because they give so much power.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know-- the first time in my life-- and the door got opened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody can help.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They was on the street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the alarm came, all of us ran to the-- it was-- they called a-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, a bomb shelter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now in German, I forgot how they called it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot a lot-- I used to speak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, Hitler was never there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was scared to come to Bremen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would killed him, because it was only marines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a port-- a port city, beautiful port city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they-- we know they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they know we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They don't know they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They throw away the passports.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they don't have the passports-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that's it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was 26 from them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they help us a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They bought me shoes, and they brought bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They was free, because they didn't know they are Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For nine months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they took us every day to Bremen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, it was in Bremen impossible to come in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They send us on farms to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on a farm fall a bomb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The bomb was-- I don't know how to-- it was double like this house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it didn't blow up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We was sitting over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was no bunker, what they called bunker in German-- a bunker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there was no bunker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were sitting, and we run the side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the bomb was laying and doesn't blow up.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
